Ngozi Mwanamwambwa Asinga (amụrụ na 25 Febụwarị na afọ 1971) bụ onye Zambia bụbu onye na-agba ọsọ
O sonyere na 100 mita, 200 mita na 400 mita ụmụ nwanyị na 1992 Summer Olympics
O mekwara asọmpi na mita 400 nke ụmụ nwanyị na 1996 Summer Olympics
Ọ bụ nwunye onye Surinam bụbu onye na-eme egwuregwu Tommy Asinga
Onye NCAA Division III All-American ugboro asaa n'okporo ụzọ, Ngozi nwetara akara atọ kachasị elu na 100, 200 na 400 mita agbụrụ, ọ bụkwa onye mmeri mba nke Division III na afọ 1992 na mita 200.
